Replot for for even more space or build a 2nd home etc. JUST 5 MINUTES TO LAKE BRIDGEPORT! Spacious Mediterranean on corner lot in beautiful Runaway Bay Subdivision. You walk into a vaulted ceiling grand foyer with office and formal dining on ether side of your grand entry. The family room with fireplace and large kitchen, granite counters, island and butlers pantry and two large pantries make this a dream work space. Spacious master and bath two walk in closets complete the first floor. Two staircases lead to three bedrooms, two baths, game room, and media room on second floor. Fresh paint inside and out in 2020, oven replaced in 2022, and the light grey inside AC unit was refurbished in 2022. This Home is a must see!!!!
